    <!-- Introduction Section -->
    <section id="introduction">
        <h2>Introduction to Value Stream Mapping (VSM)</h2>
        <p>Value Stream Mapping (VSM) is a powerful lean tool for identifying waste, improving flow, and enhancing customer satisfaction. It provides a comprehensive look at each process step and highlights areas where efficiency can be improved.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Purpose Section -->
    <section id="purpose">
        <h2>Purpose of this VSM</h2>
        <p>This project focuses on optimizing the eCommerce order fulfillment process, aiming to identify and eliminate inefficiencies to improve lead time and increase customer satisfaction.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Current State VSM Section -->
